aima.core.util.datastructure
Class XYLocation

java.lang.Object
  aima.core.util.datastructure.XYLocation

public class XYLocation
extends java.lang.Object

Note: If looking at a rectangle - the coordinate (x=0, y=0) will be the top left hand corner. This corresponds with Java's AWT coordinate system.

Author:
Ravi Mohan, Mike Stampone
